{"tid":345181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[齊做on9仔] 一人一個俾朋友搵笨經驗","createTime":"2017-08-02T22:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T23:55:05.000Z","uid":125515,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9dbcbc4a99029048fb0d95f39723930919eeae8b","tid":345181,"uid":125515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T22:43:13.000Z","msg":"先利申：自己唔係要求咩回報嘅人，但真係唔撚識做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先，借左幾萬蚊俾朋友周轉，已經過左兩三年，見佢依排又新電話又乜，先開口問佢還，佢話未有錢住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知自己on9仔已做，但個時朋友有難，自己又唔係有錢都諗住幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實到而家依一刻都仲幫緊佢搵藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8ea5e01dabfbb3f22cf1968e203f46bfa53c89","tid":345181,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T23:24:54.000Z","msg":"一借𣎴還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2010f004dbfde18330e849d46dff0694fed3be7c","tid":345181,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T23:53:58.000Z","msg":"智錢比人不嬲要簽紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9fbdb8fd49ad7a64ee88df2dff49accecda864","tid":345181,"uid":31071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T23:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借錢比人不嬲要簽紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e0238c7e22885453bb09cc197a463b5371f03465","tid":345181,"uid":125515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T23:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一人一個俾朋友搵笨經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}